        "Top-10 keywords scaled from 40 to 220 — B2B Services"
      ]
    },
    {
      "@type": "AboutPage",
      "@id": "https://seoshivam.pro/about",
      "name": "About Shivam Attri — AEO Specialist, SEO Strategist",
      "description": "Learn about Shivam Attri, AEO and SEO specialist helping B2B SaaS founders get cited by ChatGPT, Perplexity, and Google AI Overviews. 7+ years, 30+ brands, clients across US, UK, EU, AU, IN, DE.",
      "url": "https://seoshivam.pro/about",
      "isPartOf": { "@id": "https://seoshivam.pro/#website" },
      "about": { "@id": "https://seoshivam.pro/#shivam" },
      "author": { "@id": "https://seoshivam.pro/#shivam" },
      "breadcrumb": {
        "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
        "itemListElement": [
          { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://seoshivam.pro" },
          { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "About", "item": "https://seoshivam.pro/about" }
        ]
      }
    }
  ]
};

const milestones = [
  { year: '2018', tag: 'Foundation', title: 'Code meets SEO', event: 'Learned web development. HTML, CSS, WordPress. Joined a local agency as Junior Developer. Introduced to SEO. Changed how I thought about the web.' },
  { year: '2019', tag: 'First ranks', title: 'SEO fundamentals locked', event: 'Joined DAV Media as Web Designer Intern. Started ranking small businesses on Google. SEO fundamentals locked in.' },
  { year: '2020', tag: 'Volume', title: '50+ sites, patterns emerge', event: 'Worked with 50+ websites. Custom HTML, CSS, Bootstrap, WordPress across India. Volume that reveals patterns.' },
  { year: '2022', tag: 'Global', title: 'International retainer', event: 'First international client on monthly retainer. Webflow, Framer. Digital Project Manager at Emaar on international projects covering website, SEO, and social media.' },
  { year: '2024', tag: 'AEO shift', title: 'AI search before the crowd', event: 'Introduced to AI search. Started AEO implementations before most agencies acknowledged the channel existed. Cited 10+ websites in AI engines in preview mode.' },
  { year: '2025', tag: 'Scale', title: 'Four continents, real data', event: 'Scaled AEO across logistics, health tech, B2B SaaS, local businesses. US, UK, EU, AU, IN, DE clients. Real results, real data.' },
  { year: '2026', tag: 'Proof', title: 'This site is the system', event: 'Built seoshivam.pro on Astro with Claude Code. Programmatic SEO. Modern JavaScript for SEO. This site is the proof of concept. Launching it.' },
];

const differentiators = [
  {
    icon: `<svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>`,
    title: 'Not a report. A system.',
    desc: 'I build content architectures that compound every month without touching the budget. No slide decks. No reports. Actual organic growth.'
  },
  {
    icon: `<svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 8v4l3 3"/></svg>`,
    title: 'Traditional SEO and AEO simultaneously.',
    desc: 'You rank in search results and get cited by AI engines at the same time. One system. Both outcomes. Most consultants only do one.'
  },
  {
    icon: `<svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>`,
    title: 'Built for AI from day one.',
    desc: 'Every site I build includes JSON-LD, semantic HTML, and bot crawlability for GPTBot, ClaudeBot, and PerplexityBot. Not retrofitted. Built right.'
  },
];

const row1 = [
  {q:"Shivam completely restructured how we think about content. Within 3 months our organic traffic was unrecognisable and the quality of leads improved alongside the volume. He does not just do SEO. He understands the business.",n:"Founder",r:"HealthTech SaaS · India",av:"FA"},
  {q:"The first consultant who explained AEO to me in a way that made immediate business sense and then delivered on it. Our brand now appears in ChatGPT responses for our core buyer queries. That was not possible before.",n:"CEO",r:"Health Tech · US Market",av:"RC"},
  {q:"Demo requests went up 8x without touching the ad budget. He built a content system that runs itself and keeps compounding. I wish I had found him two years earlier.",n:"Marketing Lead",r:"B2B Tech · UK",av:"ML"},
  {q:"We went from invisible on Perplexity to being the cited source for our core industry terms in 45 days. That is a business advantage nobody else in our space has right now.",n:"Co-Founder",r:"FinTech Startup · US",av:"DP"},
  {q:"Shivam's AEO audit identified exactly why we were missing from AI answers despite ranking well on Google. 60 days later we were cited across 4 AI platforms. The ROI is genuinely hard to overstate.",n:"Head of SEO",r:"SaaS Platform · EU",av:"SM"},
];
const row2 = [
  {q:"Our organic leads went from 8 per month to 63 in 90 days. The content architecture Shivam built creates compounding returns every single month. No other consultant has delivered results like this for us.",n:"Marketing Director",r:"B2B Services · Canada",av:"RL"},
  {q:"I have worked with 3 SEO agencies over 5 years. Shivam is the only one who understands that the game has fundamentally changed and actually knows how to win in the new one.",n:"VP Marketing",r:"E-commerce · Australia",av:"PW"},
  {q:"The AEO strategy resulted in our brand appearing in AI responses for 12 of our 15 target buyer queries. This is what modern search looks like and Shivam was 2 years ahead of everyone else.",n:"Chief Growth Officer",r:"EdTech · India",av:"AK"},
  {q:"The web design was not just beautiful. It was structured specifically for AI crawlability from day one. We got crawled by GPTBot within 48 hours of launch. That kind of technical depth is rare.",n:"Founder",r:"Legal Tech · US",av:"JT"},
  {q:"Our content used to sit on page 3 and never move. Now it gets cited in Google AI Overviews and ChatGPT answers for logistics queries every week. Genuinely transformative work.",n:"Growth Lead",r:"Logistics · UK",av:"KH"},
