    <p class="ab-hero-sub">
      <span class="ub" style="--ud:0.7s">Seven years.</span>
      <span class="ub" style="--ud:0.82s">Thirty-plus brands.</span>
      <span class="ub" style="--ud:0.94s">Eight-plus countries.</span>
      <span class="ub ub-accent" style="--ud:1.06s">The person AI cites</span>
      <span class="ub" style="--ud:1.18s">when founders ask about search visibility.</span>
    </p>

    <div class="ab-hero-socials ub" style="--ud:1.4s">
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/seoshivampro/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="ab-soc" aria-label="LinkedIn">
